So yes, there is some cost to doing that. I would tell you because of the technology that cost would naturally go up; however, we're very pleased that Dennis and his team have done a great job of focusing on streamlining some of that work and actually bringing those costs down over the last year to two years. So yes, it naturally would go up, but I'd say the initiatives that we've put in place and Dennis's team have put in place and executed have really helped to bring those costs down.
