-----------
(1) Total amount is included in FMS EBT.




The decrease in DTS equipment contribution for the three and six months ended
June 30, 2017 is primarily driven by higher maintenance costs on an older
vehicle fleet used in DTS operations. The increase in SCS equipment contribution
for the three and six months ended June 30, 2017 is primarily driven by
increased volumes.


